snippet.title: Nimble Quest All 3-Star Characters Playthrough - Depths 2 to Sewers 4
snippet.description:
This is a hacked version of the app I found online with fully unlocked characters and lots of gold coin. Just google for 'nimble quest hacked app' and you should be able to find it, since I don't think I'm allowed to give direct links.

I complete a run from depths 2 to courtyard 4, at that point it just depends on whether you get potions to heal your party or attack boosts to keep the enemy population low. Since there isn't a real ending to the game, the purpose of this video is just to show how powerful the fully levelled crew is in clearing the map of monsters.
